<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.249407>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Clarkus papillatus (Bastian, 1865) Jairajpuri, 1970 female. A – C: Anterior end. D: Pharyngo-intestinal junction. E: Anterior genital branch. F: Posterior genital branch. G: Vulval region. H: Intestinal lumen showing two cellular bodies. I, J: Posterior body region (Scale bar = 10 µm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/249407/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

